Name: Quinoa
Description: Rich in protein, dietary fiber, B vitamins, and dietary minerals in amounts greater than in many grains.

DescriptionLocalization.es: Rico en proteínas, fibra, vitaminas B y minerales, en cantidades mayores que en muchos otros granos.
DescriptionLocalization.ko: 단백질, 식이섬유, 비타민B, 그리고 미네랄이 다른 곡물들보다 풍부합니다.
DescriptionLocalization.de: Reicher an Proteinen, Ballaststoffen, Vitamin B und Mineralstoffen als die meisten anderen Getreide.
DescriptionLocalization.fr: Plus riche en protéines, fibres, Vitamines B et minéraux que beaucoup d'autres grains.
